data.text:
Raising Victor Vargas is a 2002 tv series. It is rated TV-MA

Release date: May 16 2002- July 17 2003

Cast[]

Victor Rasuk as Victor Vargas. Main Protagonist.

Donna Maldonado as Donna. Main Deuteragonist.

Kevin Rivera as Harold. Main Character.

Krystal Rodriguez as Vicki. Main Tritagonist.

Judy Marte as Judy. Major Character.

Melonie Diaz as Melonie. Main Antagonist of season 1 and the tertiary antagonist of season 2.

Matthew Roberts as Hector. Primary Character.

Alexander Garcia as Al. Former Character.

John Ramos as Macho. Central Character.

Theresa Martinez as Judyâ€™s Mom. Supporting Character.

Altagarcia Guzman as Grandma. Recurring Character.

Silvestre Rasuk as Nino. Secondary Antagonist of season 1 and the main antagonist of season 2.

Wilfree Vasquez as Carlos. Tertiary Antagonist and the secondary antagonist of season 2.

Juan I. Lebron as Israel. Quaternary Antagonist.

Randy Luna as Pool Boy #3. Quinary Antagonist.

Jeff Knite as Pool Boy #4. Senary Antagonist.

Jacqueline Rosario as Singer. Major Antagonist.

Joe Rosario as Security Guard. Primary Antagonist.

Gladys Austin as Social Worker. Minor Antagonist.

Linda Vester as Herself. Quaternary Antagonist of Season 2.
